    <p class="section-body reveal reveal-delay-2" style="color:var(--stone)">
      At Salt &amp; Lux, we ensure your space achieves the highest level of cleanliness, delivering a serene environment for your home or office.
    </p>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="pstep reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="pnum">01</div>
        <div class="ptitle">Consultation</div>
        <div class="ptext">We assess your space and tailor a custom cleaning plan to your exact needs.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pstep reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="pnum">02</div>
        <div class="ptitle">Scheduling</div>
        <div class="ptext">Choose a time that suits your schedule — one-time or recurring.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pstep reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="pnum">03</div>
        <div class="ptitle">Deep Clean</div>
        <div class="ptext">Our trained team arrives fully equipped and executes to luxury standards.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pstep reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="pnum">04</div>
        <div class="ptitle">Inspection</div>
        <div class="ptext">Final walkthrough ensures every corner meets our exacting quality bar.</div>
